0.005   2019-07-16  Released-By: PERLANCAR; Urgency: medium

	- By default now creates temporary file in the same directory as
	  target filename, to avoid rename() failing with cross-device link
	  error when temporary directory is on a different filesystem than
	  the current one [GH #1].

        - [doc] Expand documentation.


